<paragraph id="662C43B0D779F35F25F9E78211CADA82" pageId="0" pageNumber="31">China, Yunnan Province, Jinghong City, Mengyang Town, in rotting wood in a tropical rainforest, July 2017, Z.W. Xi &amp; L. Zhang (holotype, NYNU 17934T preserved in a metabolically-inactive state), ex-holotype: CICC 33271; CBS 15231.</paragraph>
